#2: thanks anyways, i got it done, yay! No need to worry about losing my 13 a’s ina row

Nobody cares if you’re in 7th grade, it isn’t a viable excuse and it doesn’t help anyone to help you, so why would you even mention it? Exactly, no reason except immaturity. No one likes helping the immature.[/quote]
no need to talk on this anymore, the title says for it to be closed meaning there is no need to post anymore in here.
